1 information; or
2 (ii) The social media platform finds that the
3 content is sufficiently newsworthy or of other public interest to outweigh
4 the privacy interests of the minor or adult who was featured in the content
5 creator's content as a minor.
6 (d) This section does not affect a right or remedy available under any
7 other law of this state.
